metadata.name: pain bloom #254
metadata.description:
Maybe he was 16 years old when he stopped studying
And he ran away from his family three times to get to the bus that is going to death road and it is not known if he came back
It is a collection of an inner pain
Inner pain is not only physical
The new collection is about my father
When he became a veteran in the Iran-Iraq war
And its pains have remained
